 Online Marketing — broken down clearly, with everything that&#x27;s included. No hidden fees. No locked-in packages you can&#x27;t understand.</p></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex justify-end\"><img alt=\"Archie reviewing pricing\" width=\"620\" height=\"626\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[400px] xl:max-w-[440px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Pricing.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Pricing.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-Pricing.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-cream relative\"><div class=\"section-container pb-12 lg:pb-16 -mt-2\"><div class=\"max-w-[1000px] mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-navy/10 p-5 lg:p-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-4 sm:gap-5\"><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-sm lg:text-base tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-orange flex-shrink-0 sm:border-r sm:border-navy/10 sm:pr-6\">Jump to ↓</p><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 flex-1\"><a href=\"#it-pricing\" class=\"group hover:bg-cream rounded-lg px-4 py-3.5 flex items-center gap-3 transition-colors cursor-pointer\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.05rem] lg:text-[1.15rem] tracking-wide flex-1 group-hover:text-orange transition-colors leading-tight\">IT Support &amp; Security</span><span class=\"text-navy/30 group-hover:text-orange transition-colors flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></span></a><a href=\"#web-pricing\" class=\"group hover:bg-cream rounded-lg px-4 py-3.5 flex items-center gap-3 transition-colors cursor-pointer\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"2\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"12\"></line><path d=\"M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.05rem] lg:text-[1.15rem] tracking-wide flex-1 group-hover:text-orange transition-colors leading-tight\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</span><span class=\"text-navy/30 group-hover:text-orange transition-colors flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></span></a><a href=\"#marketing-pricing\" class=\"group hover:bg-cream rounded-lg px-4 py-3.5 flex items-center gap-3 transition-colors cursor-pointer\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 11l18-8v18l-18-8v-2z\"></path><path d=\"M11.6 16.8a3 3 0 1 1-5.8-1.6\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.05rem] lg:text-[1.15rem] tracking-wide flex-1 group-hover:text-orange transition-colors leading-tight\">Online Marketing</span><span class=\"text-navy/30 group-hover:text-orange transition-colors flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></span></a></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"it-pricing\" class=\"bg-cream scroll-mt-20 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"max-w-[760px] mb-12\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>IT Support &amp; Security</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-6\">Protection sized for<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">your business</span> —<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">not an enterprise budget.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text mb-3\">Priced per user, per month — so you only pay for the people who actually need coverage. All three tiers include proactive monitoring and real human support. The difference is response time, depth of security, and access.</p><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-navy/70 text-[0.9rem] tracking-wide\">3-user minimum on all packages. Month-to-month service agreement, no long-term lock-in.</p></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5\"><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl bg-white p-7 lg:p-8 flex flex-col border border-navy/10\"><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.25rem] tracking-wide mb-2\">On Watch</h3><div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-1\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[2.75rem] leading-none\">$35</span><span class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.85rem]\">/user/mo</span></div><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/50 text-xs tracking-wide mb-5\">3-user minimum</p><div class=\"bg-navy/5 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 mb-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-orange flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"curr