quirements — designed around your brand and customers.</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2.5 mb-7 flex-1\"><li class=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start text-navy/80 font-exo text-[0.92rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span><span>Full custom or WordPress build</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start text-navy/80 font-exo text-[0.92rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span><span>Designed around your brand &amp; customers</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start text-navy/80 font-exo text-[0.92rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span><span>Hosting, security &amp; maintenance included</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start text-navy/80 font-exo text-[0.92rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span><span>Same team builds and supports it</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start text-navy/80 font-exo text-[0.92rem] leading-[1.55]\"><span class=\"text-orange\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></span><span>No ongoing contract — your site is yours</span></li></ul><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-navy/55 text-xs leading-[1.5] mb-6 pt-5 border-t border-navy/10\"><span class=\"font-bold text-navy/70 uppercase tracking-wide block mb-1\">Best for</span>Businesses with specific needs or complex requirements</p><a class=\"btn justify-center w-full btn-secondary\" href=\"/contact?service=web\">Call for Details<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div></div><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.85rem] mt-8 max-w-[760px]\">Monthly packages include a simple service agreement. Custom builds require no ongoing contract — your site is yours.</p></div></section><section id=\"marketing-pricing\" class=\"bg-white scroll-mt-20 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"max-w-[760px] mb-12\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Online Marketing</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-6\">Local marketing that<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">works</span> — without the<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-navy\">agency markup</span> <!-- -->or the mystery.</h2><p class=\"body-text\">Three things that move the needle for small, local businesses: getting you found in local search, running Google Ads that earn their keep, and keeping your Google Business Profile working for you every day. Pricing starts where it makes sense and scales with your market.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 mb-12\"><div class=\"bg-cream rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 hover:border-orange/40 transition-colors p-6 lg:p-7 grid md:grid-cols-[auto_1fr_auto] gap-5 md:gap-8 items-start md:items-center\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><line x1=\"21\" y1=\"21\" x2=\"16.65\" y2=\"16.65\"></line></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.15rem] lg:text-[1.25rem] tracking-wide mb-2\">Local SEO</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.92rem] leading-[1.65]\">Foundation local search optimization — keyword targeting, on-page SEO, citation building, and monthly reporting. Includes Google Business Profile setup if needed.</p></div><div class=\"md:text-right md:border-l md:border-navy/10 md:pl-7 lg:pl-8 md:min-w-[180px]\"><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-orange text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-1\">Starting at</p><div class=\"flex items-baseline md:justify-end gap-1\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.25rem] leading-none tabular-nums\">$299</span><span class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.85rem] leading-none\">/mo</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-cream rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 hover:border-orange/40 transition-colors p-6 lg:p-7 grid md:grid-cols-[auto_1fr_auto] gap-5 md:gap-8 items-start md:items-center\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 11l18-8v18l-18-8v-2z\"></path><path d=\"M11.6 16.8a3 3 0 1 1-5.8-1.6\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.15rem] lg:text-[1.25rem] tracking-wide mb-2\">Google Ads (PPC)</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.92rem] leading-[1.65]\">Campaign setup, ongoing management, and monthly performance reporting. Ad spend billed separately, directly to your account — no markup.</p></div><div class=\"md:text-right md:border-l md:border-navy/10 md:pl-7 lg:pl-8 md:min-w-[180px]\"><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-orange text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-1\">Starting at</p><div class=\"flex items-baseline md:justify-end gap-1\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.25rem] leading-none tabular-nums\">$399</span><span class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.85rem] leading-none\">/mo + ad spend</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-cream rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 hover:border-orange/40 transition-colors p-6 lg:p-7 grid md:grid-cols-[auto_1fr_auto] gap-5 md:gap-8 items-start md:items-center\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.15rem] lg:text-[1.25rem] tracking-wide mb-2\">Google Business Profile</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.92rem] leading-[1.65]\">Profile optimization, regular posting, review monitoring, and ongoing updates. Available as a standalone service if that&#x27;s all you need.</p></div><div class=\"md:text-right md:border-l md:border-navy/10 md:pl-7 lg:pl-8 md:min-w-[180px]\"><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-orange text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-1\">Starting at</p><div class=\"flex items-baseline md:justify-end gap-1\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.25rem] leading-none tabular-nums\">$199</span><span class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.85rem] leading-none\">/mo — included with Local SEO</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-cream rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 hover:border-orange/40 transition-colors p-6 lg:p-7 grid md:grid-cols-[auto_1fr_auto] gap-5 md:gap-8 items-start md:items-center\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-orange/10 text-orange flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg width=\"26\" height=\"26\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"2\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"22\" y2=\"12\"></line><path d=\"M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[1.15rem] lg:text-[1.25rem] tracking-wide mb-2\">Google Local Services</h3><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.92rem] leading-[1.65]\">Setup and ongoing management of Google Local Services Ads — get the green Google Guaranteed badge and pay per qualified lead.</p></div><div class=\"md:text-right md:border-l md:border-navy/10 md:pl-7 lg:pl-8 md:min-w-[180px]\"><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-orange text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-1\">Starting at</p><div class=\"flex items-baseline md:justify-end gap-1\"><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.25rem] leading-none tabular-nums\">$199</span><span class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.85rem] leading-none\">/mo</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-navy rounded-2xl p-7 lg:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6\"><div class=\"md:max-w-[560px]\"><p class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-orange text-xs tracking-[0.22em] uppercase mb-2\">Not sure where to start?</p><p class=\"font-eurostile text-white uppercase text-[1.5rem] lg:text-[1.85rem] tracking-wide leading-[1.15]\">Every engagement starts with a<!-- --> <span class=\"italic text-orange\">scoping conversation</span> <!-- -->— no contracts, just clarity.</p></div><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-lg flex-shrink-0 justify-center\" href=\"/contact?service=marketing\">Talk to a Real Person <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-cream overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container py-16 lg:py-24\"><div class=\"max-w-[860px] mx-auto text-center\"><p class=\"h-section\"><span class=\"text-navy\">We<!-- --> </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">don&#x27;t charge</span> <span class=\"text-navy\">for things you<!-- --> </span><span class=\"italic text-outlined-navy\">don&#x27;t need.</span></p><p class=\"body-text max-w-[640px] mx-auto mt-6\">Every package is built around what small businesses actually use — and what they can actually afford.</p></div></div></section><section id=\"pricing-cta\" class=\"section-y scroll-mt-20 overflow-hidden bg-teal-gradient\"><div class=\"section-container\"><div class=\"max-w-[860px] mx-auto text-center\"><p class=\"eyebrow eyebrow-dark mb-5 justify-center\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>No pressure. Just clarity.</p><h2 class=\"h-section mb-6\"><span class=\"text-white\">Not sure where to start? That&#x27;s exactly what the </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">first conversation</span><span class=\"text-white\"> is for.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text body-text-dark mb-9 max-w-[620px] mx-auto\">A lot of small business owners come to us having been oversold, overcharged, or just ignored. We don&#x27;t start with a pitch — we start by understanding what you&#x27;re dealing with and what actually makes sense for your business.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-6\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-lg justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to a Real Person <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a><a class=\"btn btn-lg justify-center border border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10\" href=\"/#services\">See How We Help <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-white/55 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase\">We respond within one business day. No sales pressure, ever.</p></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-white border-t border-navy/10\"><div class=\"section-container pt-16 pb-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr_1.2fr] gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-start\"><div><img alt=\"Tech 4 Underdogs\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"180\" height=\"58\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-auto w-40 mb-4\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.9rem] leading-[1.7] max-w-[320px] mb-6\">Reliable, affordable IT, websites, and online marketing — built for the small businesses doing serious work.</p><div class=\"flex gap-2\"></div></div><div><h3 class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.8rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-5\">Navigate</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2.5\"><li><a class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/65 text-[0.9rem] hover:text-orange transition-colors flex items-center gap-2.5 leading-snug cursor-pointer\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-orange text-[8px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">■</span>Home</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/65 text-[0.9rem] hover:text-orange transition-colors flex items-center gap-2.5 leading-snug cursor-pointer\" href=\"/about\"><span class=\"text-orange text-[8px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">■</span>About</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/65 text-[0.9rem] hover:text-orange transition-colors flex items-center gap-2.5 leading-snug cursor-pointer\" href=\"/pricing\"><